<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_602" id="300r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_602_r1l2">Der Stat ʒu Wonſıdel </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_602_r1l3"><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan> <expan>fr<ex>ewnde</ex></expan> als wır eẅch nehſt <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> haben wıe vns eẅr <expan>mıtburg<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_602_r1l4">Hanns kawrhalls <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> hat etc Alſo <expan>laſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> wır eẅch <expan>wıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> . daʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_602_r1l5">vns <expan>derſ<ex>elb</ex></expan> kawrhalls ſeıd <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>eın<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>br<ex>ief</ex></expan> geſandt hat . des wır eẅch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_602_r1l6">auch eın <expan>abſchr<ex>ift</ex></expan> <expan>hıerynn<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>verſloſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>ſend<ex>en</ex></expan> / Darinn Jr wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nemen</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_602_r1l7"><expan>w<ex>er</ex>det</expan> . daʒ er vns etwas <expan>fremdıkl<ex>ich</ex></expan> ſchreıbt / Darauf <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> wır Jm </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_602_r1l8"><expan>ſchrıftl<ex>ich</ex></expan> <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> / als dıe <expan>yngeſloſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>abſchr<ex>ift</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>br<ex>iefs</ex></expan> auſʒweıſet </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_602_r1l9">Das <expan>v<ex>er</ex>künd<ex>en</ex></expan> wır eẅch alſo / Daʒ Jr <expan>denſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>mıtburg<ex>er</ex></expan> vmb </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_602_r1l10"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> wıllen <expan>vnt<ex>er</ex>weıſet</expan> als wır eẅch getrawen daʒ er ſıch des </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_602_r1l11"><expan>genüg<ex>en</ex></expan> laſſe . wan wır Jm doch glımpf vnd rechts gnug pıeten </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_602_r1l12">Denn wo wır eẅch lıeb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dıenſt etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_602_r1l13">vnd lat vns <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> eẅr <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> antwurt <expan>wıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> bey dem botten </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_602_r1l14"><expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>ſ<ex>upra</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_602" id="300r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Der stat zu Wonsidel </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>ewnde</ex></expan>, als wir ewch nehst
                                <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> haben, wie uns ewr
                                <expan>mitburg<ex>er</ex></expan> Hanns Kawrhalls
                                <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> hat etc., also
                                <expan>lass<ex>en</ex></expan> wir ewch
                            <expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan>, daz uns <expan>ders<ex>elb</ex></expan>
                        Kawrhalls seid <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ein<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>br<ex>ief</ex></expan> gesandt hat, des wir ewch auch ein
                                <expan>abschr<ex>ift</ex></expan>
<expan>hierynn<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>versloss<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>send<ex>en</ex></expan>; darinn ir wol
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nemen</expan>
<expan>w<ex>er</ex>det</expan>, daz er uns etwas
                            <expan>fremdikl<ex>ich</ex></expan> schreibt; darauf
                                <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> wir im
                            <expan>schriftl<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>, als die
                            <expan>yngesloss<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>abschr<ex>ift</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>br<ex>iefs</ex></expan> auszweiset. Das
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>künd<ex>en</ex></expan> wir ewch also, daz ir
                                <expan>dens<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>mitburg<ex>er</ex></expan> umb <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> willen
                                <expan>unt<ex>er</ex>weiset</expan>, als wir ewch getrawen, daz er
                        sich des <expan>genüg<ex>en</ex></expan> lasse, wan wir im doch glimpf und
                        rechts gnug pieten; denn wo wir ewch lieb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        dienst etc. Und lat uns <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> ewr
                                <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> antwurt
                            <expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan> bey dem botten.
                            <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>s<ex>upra</ex></expan>. </ab>
</div>
